description:
[{'description': "
Looking for a reliable, stylish, and capable SUV? The 2023 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD has everything you need for everyday drives or weekend getaways. With its sleek design and all-wheel drive performance, it's built to take on any road or weather condition.


Key Highlights:

160 Point Inspection on All Pre-Owned Inventory: Prioritize quality and reliability with our comprehensive 160-point inspection, guaranteeing that every aspect of the vehicle meets our stringent standards for your satisfaction.

Fresh MVI (Motor Vehicle Inspection) on All Units: Drive with peace of mind knowing that this vehicle has undergone a fresh MVI, meeting all safety and performance standards to ensure your safety on the road.


Key Features:

2.5L 4-Cylinder Engine: This robust engine delivers 203 horsepower and excellent fuel efficiency, providing both power and economy for any driving condition.

All-Wheel Drive (AWD): Experience ultimate traction and stability, whether you're driving in the city or tackling rugged terrains. Perfect for snowy or rainy conditions!

Heated Seats: Stay cozy on chilly days with front heated seats that add a luxurious touch to your daily drives.

Toyota Safety Sense 2.5: Equipped with advanced driver-assistance technologies, including: Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection, Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assit, Adaptive Cruise Control, and Lane Tracing Assist.

Smart Connectivity: Stay connected with a 7-inch touchscreen infotainment system that includes Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth, and USB ports, ensuring seamless integration with your devices for music, navigation, and hands-free calls.

 

Whether you're commuting, running errands, or planning a road trip, the 2023 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD is the perfect companion. Don't miss out on this reliable and versatile SUV!
 "}]

[{'description': "
Are you looking for a dependable, stylish, and versatile SUV? Look no further than this 2016 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD! Whether you're commuting to work, running errands, or exploring the great outdoors, this RAV4 has you covered with its legendary Toyota reliability and impressive performance.


 

Key Highlights:

160 Point Inspection on All Pre-Owned Inventory: Prioritize quality and reliability with our comprehensive 160-point inspection, guaranteeing that every aspect of the vehicle meets our stringent standards for your satisfaction.

Bluetooth Connectivity  Hands-free calling and audio streaming ensure you stay connected and safe while driving.

Comfortable Cloth Upholstery  High-quality fabric seats offer lasting comfort for all passengers, ideal for both long and short drives.

Ample Cargo Space  Enjoy 1,090 liters of cargo room, expandable to 2,080 liters with the rear seats folded down. Perfect for grocery runs, road trips, or transporting outdoor gear.


This RAV4 is in excellent condition and ready for many more kilometers of adventure. Toyota's unmatched reliability and low maintenance costs make this a smart and long-lasting choice.

description:
[{'description': "
Looking for an adventurous, reliable, and fuel-efficient SUV? This 2022 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD offers a perfect blend of capability, comfort, and cutting-edge technology. With its All-Wheel Drive and spacious design, this RAV4 is ready to tackle any terrainwhether it's the daily commute or your next road trip.


Key Highlights:

160 Point Inspection on All Pre-Owned Inventory: Prioritize quality and reliability with our comprehensive 160-point inspection, guaranteeing that every aspect of the vehicle meets our stringent standards for your satisfaction.

Fresh MVI (Motor Vehicle Inspection) on All Units: Drive with peace of mind knowing that this vehicle has undergone a fresh MVI, meeting all safety and performance standards to ensure your safety on the road.





Key Features:

All-Wheel Drive (AWD)  Confident handling and enhanced traction on rough terrains and in adverse weather.

2.5L 4-Cylinder Engine  Delivers a potent 203 horsepower with an impressive fuel economy

Toyota Safety Sense 2.0  Advanced safety suite with Pre-Collision System, Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assist, Adaptive Cruise Control, and more for added peace of mind.

Heated Front Seats: Stay warm and comfortable during colder drives with heated front seats, ensuring a cozy ride for you and your passengers.

7-inch Touchscreen Infotainment System  Integrated with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and Amazon Alexa for seamless Bluetooth connectivity.


This 2022 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD is practically brand new and packed with features that ensure a comfortable, safe, and efficient driving experience. Whether you're headed to the mountains or cruising around town, this RAV4 is built to handle it all.

Don't miss out! Contact us to schedule a test drive and make this versatile SUV yours today!
 "}]

description:
[{'description': "
This 2018 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD is the ideal SUV for those who want a dependable and well-rounded vehicle with Toyota's legendary reliability. With its all-wheel drive capability, spacious interior, and advanced safety features, this RAV4 is ready for commutes, road trips, and everything in between.


Key Highlights:

160 Point Inspection on All Pre-Owned Inventory: Prioritize quality and reliability with our comprehensive 160-point inspection, guaranteeing that every aspect of the vehicle meets our stringent standards for your satisfaction.

Fresh MVI (Motor Vehicle Inspection) on All Units: Drive with peace of mind knowing that this vehicle has undergone a fresh MVI, meeting all safety and performance standards to ensure your safety on the road.


Key Features:

Fuel-Efficient 2.5L 4-Cylinder Engine: Offers a perfect balance of power and fuel economy with 176 horsepower, delivering an estimated 10.5 L/100 km city and 8.1 L/100 km highway, so you can save at the pump without sacrificing performance.

All-Wheel Drive (AWD): Toyota's AWD system provides extra stability and control, making this RAV4 a confident choice in all weather conditions and on various terrains.

Heated Seats: Stay cozy on chilly days with front heated seats that add a luxurious touch to your daily drives.

Toyota Safety Sense P (TSS-P) includes Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection, Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assist, Dynamic Radar Cruise Control, Automatic High Beams, alongside with a Rearview camera that makes parking and reversing hassle-free.

6.1-Inch Touchscreen Display with AM/FM radio, CD player, Bluetooth for hands-free calling, and audio streaming, keeping you connected and entertained.


With a reputation for reliability, fuel efficiency, and safety, this 2018 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD is the perfect SUV for those who need versatility and peace of mind on every journey. Whether you're commuting or setting out for a weekend trip, this RAV4 has all the essentials for a comfortable and confident ride.
 "}]

description:
[{'description': "
Introducing the 2023 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD, engineered to take on whatever life throws at you. Whether you're commuting through the city or embarking on a weekend getaway, this compact SUV offers a smooth ride with advanced capabilities. Here's why it stands out:

 

Key Highlights:

160 Point Inspection on All Pre-Owned Inventory: Prioritize quality and reliability with our comprehensive 160-point inspection, guaranteeing that every aspect of the vehicle meets our stringent standards for your satisfaction.

Fresh MVI (Motor Vehicle Inspection) on All Units: Drive with peace of mind knowing that this vehicle has undergone a fresh MVI, meeting all safety and performance standards to ensure your safety on the road.


Key Features:

All-Wheel Drive (AWD)  Confident handling and enhanced traction on rough terrains and in adverse weather.

2.5L 4-Cylinder Engine  Delivers a potent 203 horsepower with an impressive fuel economy

Toyota Safety Sense 2.5  Advanced safety suite with Pre-Collision System, Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assist, Adaptive Cruise Control, and more for added peace of mind.

Heated Front Seats: Stay warm and comfortable during colder drives with heated front seats, ensuring a cozy ride for you and your passengers.

8-inch Touchscreen Infotainment System  Integrated with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and Amazon Alexa for seamless Bluetooth connectivity.


Drive into your next adventure with confidence in the 2023 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD. Book your test drive today!
 "}]

Reduced $3,000! RAV4 LE AWD with Apple CarPlay,Heated Seats andKeyless Entry!
 
The 2021 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD is powered by a robust 2.5L 4-cylinder engine paired with an automatic transmission, offering a blend of performance and efficiency. This engine delivers a smooth, responsive driving experience with ample power for both city and highway driving. The all-wheel-drive system enhances traction and stability, making the RAV4 a versatile choice for various weather conditions and road types.
 
Inside, the RAV4 LE provides a comfortable and spacious cabin designed for both driver and passengers. The seats are supportive and well-cushioned, ensuring a pleasant ride on long journeys or daily commutes. The interior features ample legroom and headroom, while the rear seats and cargo area offer generous space that can easily accommodate your gear, groceries, or luggage.
 
Overall, the 2021 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD combines dependable performance, comfort, and practicality in a sleek black package. With its low mileage and advanced features, this RAV4 is an excellent option for those seeking a reliable, stylish, and versatile SUV that meets a variety of driving needs.

description:
[{'description': "
Looking for a reliable, stylish, and capable SUV? The 2023 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD has everything you need for everyday drives or weekend getaways. With its sleek design and all-wheel drive performance, it's built to take on any road or weather condition.


Key Highlights:

160 Point Inspection on All Pre-Owned Inventory: Prioritize quality and reliability with our comprehensive 160-point inspection, guaranteeing that every aspect of the vehicle meets our stringent standards for your satisfaction.

Fresh MVI (Motor Vehicle Inspection) on All Units: Drive with peace of mind knowing that this vehicle has undergone a fresh MVI, meeting all safety and performance standards to ensure your safety on the road.


Key Features:

2.5L 4-Cylinder Engine: This robust engine delivers 203 horsepower and excellent fuel efficiency, providing both power and economy for any driving condition.

All-Wheel Drive (AWD): Experience ultimate traction and stability, whether you're driving in the city or tackling rugged terrains. Perfect for snowy or rainy conditions!

Heated Seats: Stay cozy on chilly days with front heated seats that add a luxurious touch to your daily drives.

Toyota Safety Sense 2.5: Equipped with advanced driver-assistance technologies, including: Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection, Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assit, Adaptive Cruise Control, and Lane Tracing Assist.

Smart Connectivity: Stay connected with a 7-inch touchscreen infotainment system that includes Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth, and USB ports, ensuring seamless integration with your devices for music, navigation, and hands-free calls.

 

Whether you're commuting, running errands, or planning a road trip, the 2023 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD is the perfect companion. Don't miss out on this reliable and versatile SUV!

 
 "}]

description:
[{'description': "
Looking for a versatile SUV that combines reliability, comfort, and advanced all-wheel drive capabilities? This 2014 Toyota RAV4 XLE AWD is the perfect match for both city and outdoor adventures! With Toyota's signature durability and efficient engineering, this RAV4 XLE has been well-maintained and is ready for its next owner.


Key Highlights:

160 Point Inspection on All Pre-Owned Inventory: Prioritize quality and reliability with our comprehensive 160-point inspection, guaranteeing that every aspect of the vehicle meets our stringent standards for your satisfaction.

Fresh MVI (Motor Vehicle Inspection) on All Units: Drive with peace of mind knowing that this vehicle has undergone a fresh MVI, meeting all safety and performance standards to ensure your safety on the road.


Key Features:

Fuel-Efficient 2.5L 4-Cylinder Engine: A balanced combination of power and fuel efficiency, with an impressive fuel economy rating of 10.7 L/100 km city / 8.1 L/100 km highway.

All-Wheel Drive (AWD): This RAV4's AWD system enhances traction and stability, making it a great choice for all weather conditions and light off-roading.

Touchscreen Infotainment: Includes a 6.1-inch touchscreen display with easy-to-use controls, AM/FM radio, CD player, Bluetooth connectivity, and six speakers for clear audio.

Power Sunroof: Enjoy the open-air experience and natural light with a tilt/slide power sunroof.

Dual-Zone Climate Control: Provides separate temperature zones for driver and passenger comfort.


Whether commuting in town or heading out for the weekend, this 2014 RAV4 XLE AWD has all the essentials and more. Don't miss out on this dependable and versatile SUV!
 "}]

description:
[{'description': "
Get ready to elevate your driving experience with this 2021 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD. This SUV offers a blend of efficiency, advanced safety features, and rugged performance to take you from daily commutes to weekend adventures with ease.


Key Highlights:

160 Point Inspection on All Pre-Owned Inventory: Prioritize quality and reliability with our comprehensive 160-point inspection, guaranteeing that every aspect of the vehicle meets our stringent standards for your satisfaction.

Fresh MVI (Motor Vehicle Inspection) on All Units: Drive with peace of mind knowing that this vehicle has undergone a fresh MVI, meeting all safety and performance standards to ensure your safety on the road.


Key Features:

2.5L 4-Cylinder Engine: This robust engine delivers 203 horsepower and excellent fuel efficiency, providing both power and economy for any driving condition.

All-Wheel Drive (AWD): Toyota's intelligent AWD system gives you the confidence to tackle all road conditions, whether it's rain, snow, or off-road terrain, with optimal traction and control.

Heated Seats: Stay cozy on chilly days with front heated seats that add a luxurious touch to your daily drives.

Toyota Safety Sense 2.0: This RAV4 is equipped with Toyota's cutting-edge safety suite, including Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection, Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assist, Dynamic Radar Cruise Control, and Automatic High Beams, making every drive safer for you and your passengers.

Smart Connectivity: Stay connected with a 7-inch touchscreen infotainment system that includes Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth, and USB ports, ensuring seamless integration with your devices for music, navigation, and hands-free calls.


This 2021 Toyota RAV4 LE AWD is the perfect choice for anyone seeking a dependable, feature-packed SUV that's ready for any adventure. Don't miss your chance to own this great vehicle!
 "}]

description: [{'description': "Our versatile 2020 Toyota RAV4 XLE AWD in Super White inspires you to seek out adventure every day! Powered by a 2.5 Liter Dynamic Force 4 Cylinder generating 203hp paired with an 8 Speed Direct Shift Automatic transmission with ECO and Sport modes so you can pick your own kind of performance. Nimble and easy to maneuver, this All Wheel Drive SUV is also efficient enough to score nearly approximately 7.1L/100km on the highway. Our popular RAV4 adds rugged good looks, too, with LED lighting, fog lamps, 17-inch alloy wheels, dual chrome exhaust outlets, and a rear spoiler for a sporty finish.Our XLE cabin encourages you to take command of each day with supportive fabric seats, eight-way power for the driver, a multifunction steering wheel, dual-zone climate control, and high-tech benefits that are anchored by an Entune infotainment system. With that, you're treated to a 7-inch touchscreen, a six-speaker sound system, voice recognition, and an impressive range of connectivity choices that include Android Auto, Apple CarPlay, Bluetooth, WiFi compatibility, and Amazon Alexa compatibility.Toyota's sophisticated Safety Sense 2.0 technology gives a boost to your peace of mind with adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assistance, and automatic braking to go with ABS, airbags, and a backup camera. Enjoy bold style for every mile in our RAV4 XLE! Low Hassle Pricing means that you dont have to be an expert negotiator to get a good, fair deal on your next used vehicle. Most of our customers have said that getting a fair price upfront is more important than the ability to negotiate the price when they are choosing where to buy a used vehicle. Low Hassle Pricing means that we have done our research and we are confident that we are well positioned in the marketplace. Toyota Safety Sense 2.5: This advanced safety suite includes features like Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection, Lane Tracing Assist, and Full-Speed Dynamic Radar Cruise Control.

8 Touchscreen Infotainment System: Seamless smartphone integration with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and Amazon Alexa, keeping you connected wherever you go.

Power Moonroof: Elevate your driving experience with fresh air and natural light.

Smart Key System with Push-Button Start: Conveniently unlock and start your car without having to take the key fob out of your pocket.


This 2023 Toyota RAV4 Hybrid XLE AWD is perfect for those who want the ruggedness of an SUV with the efficiency of a hybrid. With advanced tech, safety features, and exceptional fuel economy, it's the ideal choice for eco-conscious drivers who crave adventure.
 "}]

[{'description': "
Upgrade your driving experience with this exceptional 2020 Toyota RAV4 XLE AWD, featuring a premium sunroof and sleek leather interior! Perfect for both city streets and off-road adventures, this RAV4 is packed with top-of-the-line features for comfort, performance, and versatility.

160 Point Inspection on All Pre-Owned Inventory: Prioritize quality and reliability with our comprehensive 160-point inspection, guaranteeing that every aspect of the vehicle meets our stringent standards for your satisfaction.

Fresh MVI (Motor Vehicle Inspection) on All Units: Drive with peace of mind knowing that this vehicle has undergone a fresh MVI, meeting all safety and performance standards to ensure your safety on the road.


Key Features:

Efficient Performance: Equipped with a 2.5L 4-cylinder engine that offers an impressive blend of power and fuel economy, so you'll get both a responsive drive and savings at the pump.

All-Wheel Drive (AWD): Tackle all weather conditions with confidence, thanks to Toyota's intelligent AWD system. Designed for enhanced traction on any terrain, making it perfect for road trips or unexpected weather.

Sunroof & Leather Interior: Enjoy an elevated driving experience with a power moonroof that brings in natural light and fresh air. The cabin is appointed with high-quality leather-trimmed seating, giving you and your passengers the ultimate comfort and style.

Advanced Infotainment System: Stay connected with the Entune 3.0 Audio system, featuring a large 8-inch touchscreen display, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and Bluetooth connectivity. Access your favorite music, navigation, and apps easily on the go.

Safety First: Drive with peace of mind thanks to Toyota Safety Sense 2.0, which includes Pre-Collision System, Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assist, Dynamic Radar Cruise Control, and Road Sign Assist. Plus, a backup camera and blind-spot monitoring make maneuvering a breeze.


This 2020 Toyota RAV4 XLE AWD is in excellent condition with low mileage and a clean history. It's ready to bring comfort, style, and capability to your everyday drive or weekend adventures.
 "}]
